NK010(tha)014:0: phur pa rgyud lugs las bsnyen sgrub thams cad kyi
NK010(tha)014:1: mdzod khang rig 'dzin gzhung lam zhes bya ba bzhugs
NK010(tha)014:2: / na mahsh+r+ai badz+ra ku m+aa ra ya /
NK010(tha)014:3: 'dir phur pa rgyud lugs kyi bsnyen sgrub thams cad
NK010(tha)014:4: kyi mdzod khang rig 'dzin gzhung lam bstan pa la
NK010(tha)014:6: sbyor ba'i thog mar gnas kyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK010(tha)014:8: dang po phur pa bsgrub pa'i gnas //
NK010(tha)014:9: nags ri tsher ma can gyi shing //
NK010(tha)014:10: gcan gzan gdug pa sna tshogs yod //
NK010(tha)014:11: gnam ni ral gri mda' 'gri'i shul //
NK010(tha)014:12: sa ni gru gsum me dpung 'dra //
NK010(tha)014:13: logs la dur khrod yod pa ru //
NK010(tha)014:14: mkhas pas brtags te btsal byas na //
NK010(tha)014:15: 'di ni phur pa bsgrub gnas yin //
NK010(tha)014:17: shing gcig drung dang ma rungs pa //
NK010(tha)014:18: dug shing gdug pa yod pa dang //
NK010(tha)014:19: ma bdun gnas pa'i khyim rnams dang //
NK010(tha)014:20: srog gi rwa dang chu srin kha //
NK010(tha)014:21: g.yul ngo bkye dang mtshon phog dang //
NK010(tha)014:22: bsad bcad sa dang ma rungs sa //
NK010(tha)014:23: 'di ni drag po bsgrub pa'i gnas //
NK010(tha)014:25: de lta na'ang gnas kyi rten 'brel 'di nus pa che bas las dang po pa zer te /
NK010(tha)014:26: drod cung zad ma thob kyi ring la ha cang drag po'i gnas su gyur pa dang /
NK010(tha)014:27: gdon chen ma rung pa gnas pa'i sa ni mi legs te /
NK010(tha)014:28: sems la chos nyid mi gsal dang //
NK010(tha)014:29: nyams dang ting 'dzin g.yel bas ni //
NK010(tha)014:30: gnas 'di dag tu yongs mi bya //
NK010(tha)014:31: nam phugs rnal 'byor bdag la gnod //
NK010(tha)014:32: de bas gzhung dang mthun pa'i gnas //
NK010(tha)014:33: bkra shis sa yi gnas dag tu //
NK010(tha)014:34: yun ring bsrings na don 'grub bo //
NK010(tha)014:36: de bas na bsnyen sgrub byed pa'i gnas 'di lta bu brtag par bya ste /
NK010(tha)014:37: nags tshal chen po gang na bar //
NK010(tha)014:38: der ni legs par dpyad nas ni //
NK010(tha)014:39: klu yi mig dang 'byung po'i srang //
NK010(tha)014:40: sa yi gegs dang ma rungs sa //
NK010(tha)014:41: mi shis pa yi sa min par //
NK010(tha)014:42: las kyi bya ba gzhung bshams la //
NK010(tha)014:43: bkra shis don gyi gnas yin pas //
NK010(tha)014:45: me tog gling dang rin chen ri //
NK010(tha)014:46: dpag bsam shing dang skad snyan bya //
NK010(tha)014:47: 'bru sna tshogs dang gnam sa legs //
NK010(tha)014:48: dbyibs legs lung pa ran pa ru //
NK010(tha)014:49: bkra shis gzhung bzang gnas yin pas //
NK010(tha)014:50: gnas kyi dam pa yin par bshad //
NK010(tha)014:51: ces pa las dngos grub brnyes pa'i dam pa rnams
NK010(tha)014:52: kyis bcags pa dang gzhi bdag dkar phyogs la dad
NK010(tha)014:53: cing rgyud 'jam pa'i phyogs la brten par bya'o //
NK010(tha)014:55: yul lam sa de'i bdag po la //
NK010(tha)014:56: bden pas bkrol la sa rin bcal //
NK010(tha)014:57: zhes pas gzugs can dang rtsod pa bral bar byas la /
NK010(tha)014:59: min na gzhi bdag gtor ma barngana tshig gis bkrol
NK010(tha)014:60: la khong la'ang phan 'dogs kyi bsam pa dang ldan
NK010(tha)014:61: pas byang chub kyi sems bsgom par bya'o //
NK010(tha)014:62: de yang sngon du ston pa phun sum tshogs pa
NK010(tha)014:63: rdo rje'i slob dpon mtshan nyid dang ldan pa la
NK010(tha)014:64: / bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa rdo rje phur
NK010(tha)014:65: pa'i dbang bskur legs par mnos nas dam tshig la
NK010(tha)014:66: gnas shing bskyed rdzogs kyi lam la 'jug pa'i tshul
NK010(tha)014:67: lugs ma nor bar shes pa'i gang zag lam thun
NK010(tha)014:68: mong bas rgyud legs par 'byongs pa gang zhig gis
NK010(tha)014:69: 'gal rkyen med pa'i skabs btsal zhing gza' skar dus
NK010(tha)014:70: sbyor legs pa'i thog gnas khang la byi dor bya
NK010(tha)014:71: / / theg pa chen po'i dkon mchog spyan 'dren
NK010(tha)014:72: pa'i 'du shes bzang pos sa rgyan gnam rgyan sogs
NK010(tha)014:73: / / dang / yi dam dang chos skyong gi rten byin rlabs can dgram /
NK010(tha)014:74: de'ang rdo rje theg pa'i dam tshig gi rten cig
NK010(tha)014:75: shos rdor dril bcang dgos pas de'i mtshan nyid ni
NK010(tha)014:76: / rdo rje rtse mo lnga pa ni //
NK010(tha)014:77: lte ba pad+ma nyis bskor bya //
NK010(tha)014:78: de la nges pa'i blo can gyis //
NK010(tha)014:79: thabs kyi phyag rgya gsal bar bsam //
NK010(tha)014:80: lte ba dpal chen 'bar ba nyid //
NK010(tha)014:81: yar gyi rtse lnga sras mchog lnga //
NK010(tha)014:82: mar rtse gsang ba'i mtshan nyid do //
NK010(tha)014:84: pad+ma brgyad la khro bo bcu //
NK010(tha)014:86: ye shes 'bar ba'i rdo rje che //
NK010(tha)014:87: khro rgyal 'bar ba'i thabs kyi sku //
NK010(tha)014:88: bde chen yab rnams skur bzhugs pas //
NK010(tha)014:89: dgyes pa mchog gi phrin las mdzad du gsol //
NK010(tha)014:92: 'khar ba dang ni ljon dmar la //
NK010(tha)014:93: dril bu tshad dang ldan par bya //
NK010(tha)014:94: shes rab dag pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK010(tha)014:97: r+aa lnga rgyas 'debs yum lnga ste //
NK010(tha)014:98: lung ni b+ha ga'i mtshan nyid de //
NK010(tha)014:99: spyi bo rtse lnga lce la ni //
NK010(tha)014:100: steng 'og khro mo rnam par bsam //
NK010(tha)014:102: phyogs mtshams khro mo brgyad po bsam //
NK010(tha)014:103: rang bzhin shes rab khro tshogs rnams //
NK010(tha)014:104: rdo rje bshugs pas spyan drangs nas //
NK010(tha)014:105: shes rab ma la bstim mchod sgrub //
NK010(tha)014:106: sgra bsgrags dus gsum rgyal ba mnyes //
NK010(tha)014:107: 'gro ba'i sgrib pa dag par bsam //
NK010(tha)014:109: shes rab chen po'i rang bzhin ni //
NK010(tha)014:110: chos nyid stong pa chen po'i sgras //
NK010(tha)014:111: 'khor ba'i bag chags zil gyis gnon //
NK010(tha)014:112: dus gsum rgyal ba kun kyang mnyes //
NK010(tha)014:114: zhes de kho na nyid nges pas 'khrol ba ni rnam pa thams cad du dran par bya'o //
NK010(tha)014:115: de nas bsnyen pa'i ngo bo bdag byin gyis brlab pa'i rim pa yin pas /
NK010(tha)014:116: stegs kyi khar sgrub gtor tsaka lis brgyan pa dar nag gi gdugs can dang /
NK010(tha)014:117: dam can gyi gtor ma sha khrag gis brgyan pa /
NK010(tha)014:119: nyer spyod la sogs pa mtho dma' go rim ltar bsham /
NK010(tha)014:120: de ma thag dgos pa'i rgyal tho'i 'bul gtor dang /
NK010(tha)014:121: gzhi bdag gtor ma sogs nye bar bsdogs /
NK010(tha)014:122: bsnyen phur byug bdug brab gsum gyis gzi byin bskyed la /
NK010(tha)014:123: sgrub gtor gyi mdun du phur gdan zur gsum la gtsugs /
NK010(tha)014:124: stan 'og tu ku sha rtse mo mdun bstan cung zad kyang bzhag pa la 'dug ste /
NK010(tha)014:126: sngon 'gro thun mong bas rgyud legs par sbyangs /
NK010(tha)014:127: de nas mngon rtogs 'bring po'i gzhung bsrang ba'i tshig
NK010(tha)014:128: don 'brel ba nas bgegs gtor gyi mtshams su phyi
NK010(tha)014:129: rol ba bskrad / gu gul gyis bdug /
NK010(tha)014:133: ri rab gling bzhi'i phyogs bzhi nas //
NK010(tha)014:134: dpal dang ldan pa'i rgyal chen bzhi //
NK010(tha)014:135: phyogs srung re ba bskang ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)014:136: 'dir byin mchod sbyin gtor ma bzhes //
NK010(tha)014:137: bar du gcod pa mtshams chod cig /
NK010(tha)014:139: i dam ba lin ta kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)014:140: bi ru d+ha ka h+aum dza /
NK010(tha)014:141: i dam ba lin ta kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)014:143: i dam ba lin ta kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)014:144: bee sh+ra ba na h+aum dza /
NK010(tha)014:145: i dam ba lin ta kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)014:147: mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di bzhes la /
NK010(tha)014:148: sogs kyis gzhi bdag la bsngosa /
NK010(tha)014:149: 'di nas bzung sgo 'byed gcod phyi nang gi rgyu 'grul bcad cing /
NK010(tha)014:150: lhag par nang du sems rnam par g.yeng zhing mtshams
NK010(tha)014:151: ral na bar du gcod pa thams cad kyi rgyu
NK010(tha)014:152: ni bug sgo'i ldab ldib dang yig 'grul yin pas
NK010(tha)014:153: / mi tsher 'bags bsnyen byas pa bas lo gsum
NK010(tha)014:154: smra bcad byas pa chod che ba myong bas grub
NK010(tha)014:155: / bo // srung 'khor legs par bsgom pa gzhung bzhin no //
NK010(tha)014:160: rdzogs rim 'grub pa'i thabs su bskyed rim sgom pa yin te /
NK010(tha)014:161: rdzogs pa'i rim pa 'dod pa yis //
NK010(tha)014:162: rnal 'byor thabs ldan rnams kyis ni //
NK010(tha)014:163: bskyed pa'i rim pa rmangs nas brtsigs //
NK010(tha)014:165: srod thun nas las gzhung bsrang ba'i don la sgom
NK010(tha)014:166: don dang tshig tu 'brel bas bskyed rim gyi sbyang
NK010(tha)014:167: gzhi sbyong byed la dag pa thon par ma byas
NK010(tha)014:168: na gsang sngags zab cing thabs la mkhas pa zhes
NK010(tha)014:169: bya ba de / tshig lam dang /
NK010(tha)014:170: 'dod zhen tha mal du gol nas yon tan sna
NK010(tha)014:171: gcig kyang ma skyes par bsnyen sgrub tshad du 'khyol
NK010(tha)014:173: bzlas brjod stong 'dren du thal ba de 'byung ba'i tshul /
NK010(tha)014:175: dang por shes rab rnam gsum gyis //
NK010(tha)014:176: gtan tshigs gtan la ma phebs pas //
NK010(tha)014:177: rang bzhin med par mi shes par //
NK010(tha)014:178: dngos po mtshan ma'i chos bzung nas //
NK010(tha)014:179: theg chen khro bo'i rgyal po zer //
NK010(tha)014:180: don dam zab mo rgyab tu bor //
NK010(tha)014:181: gsang sngags zab mo bon du gyer //
NK010(tha)014:182: spyod pa spang blang dang du blangs //
NK010(tha)014:183: gti mug dbang btsan rgyu 'bras don ma rtogs //
NK010(tha)014:184: nga rgyal dbang gi rlom sems chen por bskyed //
NK010(tha)014:185: phrag dog dbang gis bdag bstod gzhan dmod byed //
NK010(tha)014:186: 'dod chags dbang gis bslus 'debs khrel 'dzem med //
NK010(tha)014:187: zhe sdang dbang gis khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bskyed //
NK010(tha)014:188: rgyud dang man ngag sgrub thabs bla mas gsang //
NK010(tha)014:189: long bas long khrid ngam grog g.yang du lhung //
NK010(tha)014:190: rnam smin bzlog par dka' ba snying re rje //
NK010(tha)014:191: zhes gsang sngags gzugs brnyan du gol ba'i rnam smin
NK010(tha)014:192: gyis r+au dra dang gdon gyi lus rten 'grub pa
NK010(tha)014:194: khro bo rang rgyud r+au dra ste //
NK010(tha)014:195: r+au dra rang rgyud khams gsum 'khor //
NK010(tha)014:197: de bas na gzhi stong nyid snying rje chen po /
NK010(tha)014:198: lam bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug tu 'brel bas 'bras bu
NK010(tha)014:199: sku gnyis mngon du byed pa'i don bskyed rim gyi
NK010(tha)014:200: rnam bshad dang bla ma'i man ngag las byung ba
NK010(tha)014:201: bzhin rgyud thog tu 'byor ba la bslab /
NK010(tha)014:203: 'bru dgu ma nor bdun khri bzlas //
NK010(tha)014:204: 'khor la de yi phyed phyed do //
NK010(tha)014:205: rab 'bring tha ma'i rtags tshang na //
NK010(tha)014:206: dngos grub blang bar shes par bya //
NK010(tha)014:207: zhes gtso 'khor 'gros sbyar ba'i dbang du bshad pa
NK010(tha)014:208: ltar ma nus na 'bru dgu pa bsgrub pa'i dus
NK010(tha)014:210: de yang lus bzlas bgrang 'phreng la brten /
NK010(tha)014:211: ngag bzlas lce mchu la brten /
NK010(tha)014:212: yid bzlas dzapa dgongs la brten pa'i phyir /
NK010(tha)014:213: bzlas pa'i mgor phreng ba byin brlab bya zhing /
NK010(tha)014:214: phreng ba'i de kho na nyid nges par bya ba'ang /
NK010(tha)014:216: yang na gdug pa tsher ma'i shing //
NK010(tha)014:217: phreng ba chen po brgya rtsa ni //
NK010(tha)014:218: ba su ta'am rgyus chen la //
NK010(tha)014:219: dgu sgril dag tu byas nas ni //
NK010(tha)014:220: brgyus pa'i mod la phur pa gdags //
NK010(tha)014:221: mthe bong mthe chung bar gyis bgrang //
NK010(tha)014:222: bdag nyid mi phyed dpal yin te //
NK010(tha)014:223: phur pa sras mchog k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)014:224: phreng ba yi ge 'bru dgu ste //
NK010(tha)014:225: phreng thag dbugs kyi rta nyid do //
NK010(tha)014:227: mgal me klad la bskor ba'am //
NK010(tha)014:228: lcags kyi tsh+wa tsh+wa brdabs pa bzhin //
NK010(tha)014:229: phar spro tshur bsdu rgyun mi gcad //
NK010(tha)014:230: bgrang phreng de nyid don la gnas //
NK010(tha)014:232: ngag bzlas la sgra bcas dang shub bu gnyis las /
NK010(tha)014:233: dang po la gsang sgrog gi nyes pa dang /
NK010(tha)014:234: gnyis pa la tshor ba btang snyoms 'byung nye bas
NK010(tha)014:235: yid bzlas dang shub bu'i bzlas pa thabs shes zung
NK010(tha)014:236: 'jug tu bgrangs pas 'du shes lung ma bstan las
NK010(tha)014:237: ldog pa'o // de'i tshe sngags ma dag pa la sogs bzlas pa'i skyon drug spang pa'ang /
NK010(tha)014:238: rgyud rnams kun gyi sngags rnams kun //
NK010(tha)014:239: sngags mkhan mkhas pas btu bar bya //
NK010(tha)014:240: shad dang tsheg bar ma nor ba //
NK010(tha)014:241: g.yal dang sbrid pas bar ma gcad //
NK010(tha)014:242: gnyid chang le lo spangs la bya //
NK010(tha)014:243: yang dag don gyi bzlas pa yin //
NK010(tha)014:245: de la dzapa dgongs dang 'od zer spro bsdu la
NK010(tha)014:246: thog ma nas ha cang mi bsgrim par dang po
NK010(tha)014:247: bskyed rim kho na la shes pa 'jur /
NK010(tha)014:248: shin tu gsal dka' na bris sku la bltas nas yid yul du longs pa dang /
NK010(tha)014:249: de snang la rang bzhin med par stsal sbyong bzhin du bzla ba'i tshul /
NK010(tha)014:250: sngags kyi 'bru ni lha yin te //
NK010(tha)014:251: lha rnams gsal la rtog pa med //
NK010(tha)014:253: bskyed rim wa la gyis gsal nas dzapa dgongs dang
NK010(tha)014:254: 'od zer spro bsdu la slob pa re mos su
NK010(tha)014:255: bya / de'i tshul ni sgrub thabs chen mor gsal ba bzhin las bdag mdun gyi tha snyad dang /
NK010(tha)014:256: do li'i bzlas pa ni bsgrub pa chen po'i khongs
NK010(tha)014:257: nas bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi ka rdzogs par byed
NK010(tha)014:258: pa'i dbang du bshad pas 'dir de'i sgos chos gnyis
NK010(tha)014:260: de yang sems can thams cad la bder gshegs snying pos ma khyab pa med na /
NK010(tha)014:261: snying po de tshogs brgyad 'dus byas pas glo bur
NK010(tha)014:262: du bslad nas 'khor ba mtha' med par sngar 'khor
NK010(tha)014:264: de las thar pa'i phyir gsang sngags rdo rje theg par lam bskyed rdzogs gnyis su gsungs /
NK010(tha)014:265: de gnyis kyang gcig la gcig ltos kyi 'brel pa can gyis zung 'jug tu ma bsgrubs na /
NK010(tha)014:266: bskyed rim rkyang pas rtag mtha' /
NK010(tha)014:267: rdzogs rim rkyang pas chad mtha' sel mi nus pa la dgongs nas thabs shes 'brel ba'am /
NK010(tha)014:269: de'ang snang ba'i 'khrul 'dzin sbyong ba la thabs bskyed pa'i rim pa /
NK010(tha)014:270: bskyed rim gyi bden zhen 'jig pa la shes rab
NK010(tha)014:271: rdzogs pa'i rim pas rgyas thebs pa ni chu zla'am
NK010(tha)014:272: / sgyu ma lta bu'i dpes mtshon la /
NK010(tha)014:273: de las snang ba zhes bya ba mig shes kyi
NK010(tha)014:274: ngor snang ba'i bstan yod thogs bcas gcig po la
NK010(tha)014:275: ngos mi gzung / las snga mas bzhag pa'i bag chags kyis bgos shing /
NK010(tha)014:276: phyi ma nye bar len pa'i gzung 'dzin rang rgyud
NK010(tha)014:277: par 'char ba'i bstan med thogs bcas thams cad de
NK010(tha)014:278: / kun 'byung gi rgyu las rnam rtog rang dgar
NK010(tha)014:279: 'char ba'i snang yul mtha' dag rten gzhal yas khang
NK010(tha)014:280: / dang / brten pa lha'i 'khor lo 'char ba
NK010(tha)014:281: la rtag tu goms par byas na lha'i snang cha
NK010(tha)014:282: des bsod nams kyi tshogs dang /
NK010(tha)014:283: de'i chos nyid rang bzhin med par rtogs pa des
NK010(tha)014:284: ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs nas skye ba 'di nyid
NK010(tha)014:285: la rnam smin rig 'dzin gyi go 'phang la sbyor
NK010(tha)014:286: zhing bar dor phyag rgya'i rig 'dzin 'grub pa'i tshul
NK010(tha)014:287: bkod pa'i le'u gnyis pa las /
NK010(tha)014:288: de nas rjes su rnal 'byor pas //
NK010(tha)014:289: lam 'di dag la dgod par bya //
NK010(tha)014:290: tshogs lam sbyor lam mthong ba'i lam //
NK010(tha)014:291: sgom lam dang ni rnam grol lam //
NK010(tha)014:292: bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sa //
NK010(tha)014:293: bcu gnyis pad+ma can gyi sa //
NK010(tha)014:294: 'khor lo tshogs chen bcu gsum pa //
NK010(tha)014:295: kun bzang bcu bzhi pa ru grags //
NK010(tha)014:296: dang po'i sa nas rig 'dzin te //
NK010(tha)014:297: gnyis pa tshe la dbang rig 'dzin //
NK010(tha)014:298: kun rdzob phyag rgya'i rig 'dzin te //
NK010(tha)014:299: rtogs pa lhun grub rig 'dzin no //
NK010(tha)014:300: phur bu'i rang bzhin don rtogs pa //
NK010(tha)014:301: rigs dag tu ni yang dag bshad //
NK010(tha)014:302: las byas sngon gyi tshogs kyis so //
NK010(tha)014:303: las bdun byas pas sbyor ba'o //
NK010(tha)014:304: de nyid bsgoms pas mthong ba dang //
NK010(tha)014:305: 'byung ba lnga dang lha yi gnas //
NK010(tha)014:306: gdan dang bcas pas bskyed par bsgom //
NK010(tha)014:307: srog nyid ye shes rgyur gnas pas //
NK010(tha)014:308: bdud bzhi las ni rnam par grol //
NK010(tha)014:309: dkyil 'khor gsum la sogs mtshan nyid //
NK010(tha)014:310: phung por ma grub pa dang 'od //
NK010(tha)014:311: gong bur gnas dang 'chi bdag dang //
NK010(tha)014:312: yi ges nyon mongs med par sbyangs //
NK010(tha)014:313: snang srid grags pa can dang ni //
NK010(tha)014:314: mi snang bar bcas lha bdud bcom //
NK010(tha)014:315: nyes ldan srog gi dbang po dang //
NK010(tha)014:316: gdags gzhi drug dang snang ba ste //
NK010(tha)014:317: gnas skabs dag la rab tu grags //
NK010(tha)014:318: dus dang grangs dang mtshan ma yi //
NK010(tha)014:319: bsnyen pa dag tu bshad pa yin //
NK010(tha)014:321: de yang las byas la sogs pa'i rkang pa gsum gyis bsnyen pa'i don bstan pa'ang /
NK010(tha)014:322: dang po rang rgyud la sngon yod dang da ltar
NK010(tha)014:323: ba'i bsod nams kyi tshogs bskrun pa tshogs lam dang
NK010(tha)014:324: / gnyis pa rdo rje slob dpon bkur te dbang
NK010(tha)014:325: bskur nod pa nas bskyed rdzogs kyi lam la 'jug
NK010(tha)014:326: pa'i bya ba mtha' dag las bdun gyi sgras bsdus
NK010(tha)014:328: rgyu de dag las sems nyid lha'i skur smin te
NK010(tha)014:329: rnam smin rig 'dzin gyi ldang tshad rdzogs pa ni
NK010(tha)014:330: mthong ba'i lam mo zhes bdag nyid kyis rtogs pa'i
NK010(tha)014:331: tshul lo // 'di ltar ma rtogs bzhin du 'od
NK010(tha)014:332: zer spro bsdu tha ga pa'i brkyang bskum lta bus
NK010(tha)014:333: sems 'khrul snang gi gzeb tu bcug pa'i bsnyen yig
NK010(tha)014:334: ni gzung 'dzin gyi rtod phur du mthong ngo //
NK010(tha)014:335: rgyu des na bsnyen pa'i skabs 'dir dam tshig gi rten tsam du bsnyen phur bzhag pa las /
NK010(tha)014:336: bsgrub bya'i ngos nas snang grags rig gsum lha'i dkyil
NK010(tha)014:337: 'khor gcig tu 'char ba la bslab pa'i phyir bsnyen
NK010(tha)014:338: phur lhar ched du gsal ba la sogs pa'i rnam
NK010(tha)014:339: shes gud du mi gcad la /
NK010(tha)014:340: thun bzhi'i mtshams 'jog kha thams cad du mchog bstod
NK010(tha)014:341: mthar dbyangs gsal yig brgya dang sbrel nas bzlas pas
NK010(tha)014:342: nyes byas bshags shing dag pa'i snod bcud la rtag
NK010(tha)014:343: mtha' gzhig pa'i nyer bsdu dang chad mtha' gzhig pa'i
NK010(tha)014:344: thun mtshams kyi lhar ldang ba ni nges par gces
NK010(tha)014:345: la / thun tha ma la tshogs mchod re grub na legs shing /
NK010(tha)014:346: ji ltar yang phur srung la sogs pa'i chos skyong la gtor 'bul dang phrin bcol bya'o //
NK010(tha)014:347: de la thun so so nas mngon rtogs mi dgos
NK010(tha)014:348: pa snga 'gyur gyi lugs so zhes mtha' gcig tu
NK010(tha)014:349: gleng ba'ang bzang por ma mthong ste las dang po
NK010(tha)014:350: pa zer kyang don la bskyed rim gyi sbyang gzhi
NK010(tha)014:351: sbyong byed lhongs su ma gyur zhing /
NK010(tha)014:352: snying po dran pa tsam gyis mngon rtogs yid yul
NK010(tha)014:353: du lhun gyis mi grub pa rnams la khyed kyang
NK010(tha)014:354: nus pa thob pa'i gang zag rdzogs pa chen po'o
NK010(tha)014:355: zhes glen pa bran pa'i phyir ro //
NK010(tha)014:356: de bas na mngon rtogs lan re'i mtshan nyid la phan yon dpag tu med pa'i tshul /
NK010(tha)014:358: mchod bstod cho ga gzhung bzhin la //
NK010(tha)014:359: sbyin dang tshul khrims bzod brtson 'grus //
NK010(tha)014:360: bsam gtan shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK010(tha)014:361: de las ldog med ma yengs pas //
NK010(tha)014:362: dngos grub myur du thob par nges //
NK010(tha)014:363: zhes pa'i don la rmongs pa'o //
NK010(tha)014:364: gnyis pa nyer bsgrub la gnyis /
NK010(tha)014:365: rten 'brel la brten nas srid pa phur bur bsgrub pa dang /
NK010(tha)014:366: rnam byang la brten nas srid pa phur bur bsgrub pa'o //
NK010(tha)014:368: dkyil 'khor yongs rdzogs kyi bdag nyid bsnyen phur dang 'brel bar bya ste /
NK010(tha)014:369: de yang bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK010(tha)014:370: phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi bar las rnam par rgyal ba la rgyab kyis phyogs shing /
NK010(tha)014:371: gtso bo la mdun gyis phyogs pa'i phur pa rdzas
NK010(tha)014:372: kyi dkyil 'khor gyi mtshan nyid shes par bya ba'ang
NK010(tha)014:373: rgyud las / rgya mdud dang po'i gzhal yas la //
NK010(tha)014:374: rigs lnga'i rgyal ba 'khor dang bcas //
NK010(tha)014:375: spyi'am rtse na yab yum gnyis //
NK010(tha)014:376: rgya mdud 'og ma'i gzhal yas na //
NK010(tha)014:378: zur brgyad khro bo phra men ma //
NK010(tha)014:379: bcu gnyis srung ma zur gsum la'o //
NK010(tha)014:380: sgo ma bzhi ni rtsibs mchan la //
NK010(tha)014:381: zhes pa ltar bsnyen phur de nyid dkyil 'khor yongs rdzogs kyi bdag nyid du gsal btab la /
NK010(tha)014:382: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa kun //
NK010(tha)014:383: thugs kyi ye shes phur bu yis //
NK010(tha)014:384: khams gsum gdar sha bcad pa dang //
NK010(tha)014:385: srid pa phur bur bsgrub par bya //
NK010(tha)014:386: zhes myang 'das las gsungs pa'i don bdag mdun gnyis ka'i thugs srog las 'od zer 'phros /
NK010(tha)014:387: srid pa gsum gyi brtan g.yo snod bcud dang bcas pa la phog par 'od du mer gyis zhu /
NK010(tha)014:388: gzugs med kyi cha rgya mdud gong ma /
NK010(tha)014:390: 'dod khams dbal gsham la thim pas srid pa'i rang
NK010(tha)014:391: bzhin rdo rje phur pa'i dkyil 'khor du rdzogs pa
NK010(tha)014:392: la gsal brtan gyi tshad brgyad ma thob bar du
NK010(tha)014:394: srid pa rdo rjer bsgrub pa zhes pa'i de kho na nyid la mngon sum du sbyar /
NK010(tha)014:395: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba las skye zhing mched pa dang /
NK010(tha)014:396: 'pho zhing 'jig par byed pas srid pa gsum du
NK010(tha)014:397: nying mtshams sbyor ba'i rten 'brel 'gags pa'i bskyed rim
NK010(tha)014:399: rnam dag dran pa'i ngang nas yig 'bru bcu bzhi
NK010(tha)014:400: pa bzla zhing re 'ga' do li la rtsal sbyangs
NK010(tha)014:401: pas dang por ye shes lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi
NK010(tha)014:403: gnyis par de'i nus pa je cher bskyed /
NK010(tha)014:405: bzhi par 'khrul snang las skyes pa'i srid pa thams
NK010(tha)014:406: cad phur pa'i rang bzhin du bsgrub pa'i nus pa
NK010(tha)014:407: thob pa'i tshul / dkyil 'khor gsum gyi bskyed rim ni //
NK010(tha)014:408: dang por thun du bcad nas bsgom //
NK010(tha)014:409: nus pa 'jug dang nus pa bskyed //
NK010(tha)014:410: nus pa brten nas nus pa thob //
NK010(tha)014:411: nus pas bzhi pa thob nas ni //
NK010(tha)014:412: gar mkhan lag pa ji bzhin du //
NK010(tha)014:413: gang ltar byas pa de ltar snang //
NK010(tha)014:415: gnyis pa rnam byang gi sgo nas srid pa phur bur bsgrub pa ni /
NK010(tha)014:417: 'dzab bzlas rnam pa du ma yang //
NK010(tha)014:418: phyi nang gsang ba gsum du 'dus //
NK010(tha)014:419: phyi yi bsgrub bya bsnyen pa dang //
NK010(tha)014:420: nang gi rang sems sbyang ba dang //
NK010(tha)014:421: gsang ba dngos grub blang ba'o //
NK010(tha)014:423: nang rang sems gzung 'dzin gyis bslad pa'i 'khrul snang
NK010(tha)014:424: gi rang gzugs lha'i de kho na nyid la brten
NK010(tha)014:425: nas sbyangs kyang / sbyong byed kyi lha de nyid
NK010(tha)014:426: rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyi rol pa rang rgyud par
NK010(tha)014:427: gzung na bskyed rim gyi rnam pa gsal kyang 'khor
NK010(tha)014:428: ba'i rang bzhin las ldog pa med pas na chos
NK010(tha)014:429: nyid rnam dag gi rol pa tsam du shes dgos
NK010(tha)014:430: nas sbyangs kyang / pa'i tshul / rtsa ba sems kyi snang gzhi la //
NK010(tha)014:431: lha yi rol pa cir snang yang //
NK010(tha)014:432: rol pa rang rgyud gzung ba na //
NK010(tha)014:433: lha yang rang rgyud dag las bskyed //
NK010(tha)014:434: bem po tho yor ril po dang //
NK010(tha)014:435: nga bdag gzung 'dzin ther zug go //
NK010(tha)014:436: rang rgyud 'dzin pa ma skyes na //
NK010(tha)014:437: ji ltar byas kyang rol pa yin //
NK010(tha)014:438: rol pa phyogs med kun la shar //
NK010(tha)014:439: de nyid sangs rgyas byang chub sems //
NK010(tha)014:440: yang dag don nyid de ru rtogs //
NK010(tha)014:442: de lta mod kyis goms pa gdeng du ma gyur
NK010(tha)014:443: gyi ring la kun tu btags pa can gyi bskyed
NK010(tha)014:445: de'i gnyen por gzung 'dzin las 'das pa'i chos nyid
NK010(tha)014:446: brjod bral gyi gnas lugs dran par byas nas de'i
NK010(tha)014:447: snang cha rten dang brten par rang shar ba la
NK010(tha)014:448: goms su bcug pas rnam pa gsal kyang rang gi
NK010(tha)014:449: ngo bos ma grub pa'i bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug lha
NK010(tha)014:450: dang bla ma'i byin rlabs 'pho ba'i stabs kyis thob
NK010(tha)014:451: pa ni sngags kyi khyad chos bla na med pa
NK010(tha)014:453: rdo rje phur pa'i snang ba la //
NK010(tha)014:454: snang ba'i chos rnams kun 'byung yang //
NK010(tha)014:455: rang rgyud grub pa ye nas med //
NK010(tha)014:456: rol pa rnam gnyis lha yi sku //
NK010(tha)014:457: lha nyid nges par gzung du med //
NK010(tha)014:458: ngos bzung bral ba'i lha nyid ni //
NK010(tha)014:459: cir yang 'gyur zhing cir yang snang //
NK010(tha)014:461: de lta bu'i bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug gi lam ma
NK010(tha)014:462: nor ba la ring du goms pa brtan pa las
NK010(tha)014:463: khams gsum du 'khor ba'i rgyu kun gzhi las rlung
NK010(tha)014:464: dang bcas pa ye shes kyi bdag nyid chen por
NK010(tha)014:465: gnas gyur pas rig 'dzin bzhis sa bcad pa'i sa
NK010(tha)014:466: lam mthon po'i yon tan 'thob nas bdud bzhi bcom
NK010(tha)014:467: pa'i tshul sngon du dkyus la drangs zin la /
NK010(tha)014:468: mthar gyis bskyed rim gyi spros pa med dgag gi
NK010(tha)014:469: blos spangs pa ma yin par rang bzhin yongs grub
NK010(tha)014:470: chos kyi dbyings su rnam par byang ba'i tshe chos
NK010(tha)014:471: nyid kyi phur bu'i gnas lugs rtogs pa ste bkod
NK010(tha)014:473: de la chos nyid phur pa ni //
NK010(tha)014:474: chos can gang la'ang ma dmigs shing //
NK010(tha)014:475: ma bcos ngang du thams cad 'dus //
NK010(tha)014:476: phur pa zhes ni de la bya //
NK010(tha)014:477: de la sems kyi phur pa ni //
NK010(tha)014:478: skye mched khams la mi gnas shing //
NK010(tha)014:479: rang byung ngang du thams cad 'dus //
NK010(tha)014:480: phur pa zhes ni de la bya //
NK010(tha)014:481: de la nam mkha'i phur pa ni //
NK010(tha)014:482: kha dog dbyibs la mi gnas shing //
NK010(tha)014:483: khyab gdal ngang du thams cad 'dus //
NK010(tha)014:484: phur bu zhes ni de la bya //
NK010(tha)014:485: de gsum dbyer med mya ngan 'das //
NK010(tha)014:486: zhes pa la sogs rgya cher yod do //
NK010(tha)014:487: gnad 'di ni ye shes lha'i gnang ba thob pa
NK010(tha)014:488: las byung ste rgyud kyi rdo rje'i gnas chen po
NK010(tha)014:489: sngon chad phal gyis ma rtogs pa zhig yin pas
NK010(tha)014:490: smin par slob pa rnams nyams su longs shig /
NK010(tha)014:491: de lta bu'i thun mtshams kyi bya ba ni bsnyen pa'i skabs dang 'dra la /
NK010(tha)014:492: 'on kyang bzlas brjod phun sum tshogs pa'i le'u las /
NK010(tha)014:493: phur pa'i khro bo las ci 'dra ba zhig byung
NK010(tha)014:494: ste phyogs bcu thams cad du sems can gyi don
NK010(tha)014:495: byas nas phur pa la bstim /
NK010(tha)014:497: phur pa nyid snying ga'i h+aum la bsdus la /
NK010(tha)014:498: 'di ni bzlas brjod phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK010(tha)014:499: zhes pa ltar thun 'jog khar sems bskyed kyi 'phen
NK010(tha)014:500: pa'i dbang gis gzhan don la 'jug pa'i dmigs pa'ang
NK010(tha)014:502: grangs dus mtshan ma'i bsnyen tshad ni /
NK010(tha)014:503: mtshan ma'i bsnyen pa'i dus tshod ni //
NK010(tha)014:504: rab kyis zla gcig gis ni 'grub //
NK010(tha)014:506: tha mas lo gsum dag na 'grub //
NK010(tha)014:509: sa ya drug 'bum bsnyen pa'i tshad //
NK010(tha)014:510: ces pas las rung 'bum phrag bcu drug /
NK010(tha)014:511: dus bsnyen de yi bzhi 'gyur ro //
NK010(tha)014:512: skabs 'dir bsnyen pa kha skong bcu cha'i sbyin sreg
NK010(tha)014:513: bya zhing de la dgang blugs kyi tshad dang mtshan
NK010(tha)014:515: dgang gzar blug gzar so so'i dbyibs //
NK010(tha)014:516: yu ba khru gang tshad du bya //
NK010(tha)014:517: dgang gzar sor bzhi sor gnyis zabs //
NK010(tha)014:518: kha ran sor gcig dkyil rin chen //
NK010(tha)014:519: ngos la yi ge 'bar ba bsgom //
NK010(tha)014:520: blug gzar sor gnyis sor gcig zabs //
NK010(tha)014:521: kha 'khor sor gcig dkyil rdo rje //
NK010(tha)014:522: ngos la yi ge rnams bsgom mo //
NK010(tha)014:524: sngags ni yig 'bru bcu bzhi pa rang rkyang las khong khra 'jug pa sogs mi dgos /
NK010(tha)014:525: rtsa ba'i sa bcad gnyis pa bsgrub pa ni /
NK010(tha)014:527: ras bris sogs la rten nus na so so'i sgos
NK010(tha)014:528: chos kyi 'dor len dang bcas pas mtshan ma rdzas
NK010(tha)014:529: kyi dkyil 'khor 'du byas pa'i steng du phur cha
NK010(tha)014:530: dgod pa'i tshul / ri rtse gangs phug g.ya' rtse'am //
NK010(tha)014:531: brag dang chu 'thab dur khrod dam //
NK010(tha)014:532: sdong gcig shing ngam brag nag gam //
NK010(tha)014:533: yang na nyams dag'i gnas su bya //
NK010(tha)014:534: sa yi ro lnga med pa ru //
NK010(tha)014:535: sngon gyi las rnams tshang byas te //
NK010(tha)014:536: zhes pas 'bru'i tshom bu'i mdun du nyer spyod dang sa lha'i gtor ma bshams la /
NK010(tha)014:538: sngon tshe dbang mdzad lha mo la //
NK010(tha)014:539: spyan drangs mchod de gsol ba ni //
NK010(tha)014:540: bar chad bgegs rnams zhi ba dang //
NK010(tha)014:541: sa yi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)014:542: b+h+au mi pa ti sa pa ri w+aa ras gtor ma phul la gshegs /
NK010(tha)014:543: swa b+h+aa wa 'i sngags don dran pas gzung ba tsam bya /
NK010(tha)014:545: skyang nul chag chag go ma ye //
NK010(tha)014:546: tshon dang srad bu byin gyis rlobs //
NK010(tha)014:547: gnam thig sa thig gsher thig gsum //
NK010(tha)014:548: bye brag so sor shes par bya //
NK010(tha)014:549: shes rab ma yis thig skud gzung //
NK010(tha)014:550: mtshams dang steng 'og tshul bzhin bya //
NK010(tha)014:551: thig chen rnam pa brgyad du btab //
NK010(tha)014:552: 'khor lo'i rtsibs brgyad e ru bcas //
NK010(tha)014:553: zla gam gsum dang rtsibs su bcas //
NK010(tha)014:554: bar khyams sgo khyams gnyis su brtags //
NK010(tha)014:555: sgo brgyad ya phubs rta babs dang //
NK010(tha)014:556: d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed d+r+wa ba dang //
NK010(tha)014:557: rgyan gyi rnam pa thams cad bya //
NK010(tha)014:559: rnam par rgyal ba la sogs pa //
NK010(tha)014:560: shar nas brtsam ste dgod par bya //
NK010(tha)014:561: dbus kyi e la bdud 'dul te //
NK010(tha)014:562: mdun rgyab g.yas g.yon grwa zur bzhi //
NK010(tha)014:563: steng 'og khro bo phra men bzhi //
NK010(tha)014:564: rim bzhin du ni dgod par bya //
NK010(tha)014:565: de yi 'khor lo'i gong ras la //
NK010(tha)014:566: phra men byin po dgod par bya //
NK010(tha)014:567: zla gam la ni sras mchog gsum //
NK010(tha)014:568: khyams la ke seng spel mar dgod //
NK010(tha)014:569: sgo bzhir srung ma bcu gnyis so //
NK010(tha)014:570: lcags ri la ni dbang phyug ma //
NK010(tha)014:571: de ltar dkyil 'khor rdzogs pa dang //
NK010(tha)014:572: byin gyis brlabs pa'i phur pa kun //
NK010(tha)014:573: bye brag so sor shes par bya //
NK010(tha)014:574: dang po chos skur byin brlab dang //
NK010(tha)014:575: de nas longs skur byin brlab dang //
NK010(tha)014:576: de nas sprul skur byin gyis rlobs //
NK010(tha)014:577: sku mchog sprul sku mngon byang chub //
NK010(tha)014:578: de nas byin brlab dbang bskur bya //
NK010(tha)014:579: mtshams kyi phur pa mnga' gsol ba'i //
NK010(tha)014:580: phur pa bcu yang byin gyis brlab //
NK010(tha)014:581: bsgrub pa'i phur pa re re la //
NK010(tha)014:582: dar gyi cod pan re re gdags //
NK010(tha)014:583: spyan drangs gzhugs gsol gnyis med bstim //
NK010(tha)014:584: byug bdug brdeg pa'i las rnams bya //
NK010(tha)014:585: de nas man+dala steng du dgod //
NK010(tha)014:586: ces dkyil 'khor gnyis rim dang chig rkyang gnyis ka
NK010(tha)014:587: gsungs pas gang bde byas pa la lha mtshan dang
NK010(tha)014:588: phur cha dgod / gal te ku su lu pa'i bsgrub pa byed na /
NK010(tha)014:589: thod pa'am rin po che'i snod 'brus bkang ba'i nang
NK010(tha)014:590: du phur cha rgyas bsdus ji ltar 'byor ba dang
NK010(tha)014:591: / ma 'byor na gtso bo dang las phur gnyis la bsdus pas rung ste /
NK010(tha)014:592: me tog tshom bu rab tu dgram //
NK010(tha)014:593: sbams pa'i phur bur rab tu dgod //
NK010(tha)014:596: dkyil 'khor mdun du many+dzi'i khri la sgrub gtor /
NK010(tha)014:604: byang du zhal zas te gor mchod dang /
NK010(tha)014:612: thod rnga dang gsang ba'i rnge'u chung sogs kyang bsham /
NK010(tha)014:615: mchod dang stob pa'i rdzas su bzhag /
NK010(tha)014:616: dza gad tshe dang tshim byed gsum //
NK010(tha)014:617: kun tu rgyu dang gal phyi lnga //
NK010(tha)014:618: ka ra ti dang zla tshes bdun //
NK010(tha)014:619: zla phrom zla rgyas m+aam sa gsum //
NK010(tha)014:620: sgrub pa tshogs kyi rdzas su bsag /
NK010(tha)014:621: dmar gyi rak+ta zo ba gang //
NK010(tha)014:622: ma mo mkha' 'gro brten pa'i rdzas //
NK010(tha)014:624: srod thun nas 'go brtsams te thun bzhir las gzhung bsdus pa bsrang /
NK010(tha)014:625: de yang nub dang por mngon rtogs rgyas pas sgom nus na legs /
NK010(tha)014:626: mi nus na sngon 'gro rnams rdzogs par blangs nas
NK010(tha)014:627: srung 'khor rnams kyi dmigs pa gtan du dgos te
NK010(tha)014:631: phal pa rnams la mi bklub 'jug /
NK010(tha)014:633: yul brgyud gang zag brgyud par byed //
NK010(tha)014:634: skye ba brgyud dang sprul pa brgyud //
NK010(tha)014:635: dngos por brgyud nas gnod par byed //
NK010(tha)014:636: bslu zhing ngo sbed sna tshogs ston //
NK010(tha)014:638: de yang bskyed rim gyi dus bdag bskyed kyi gtso bo dang /
NK010(tha)014:639: khro bo rnam rgyal gyi bar du mdun bskyed kyi
NK010(tha)014:640: gzhal yas khang brten pa'i lha dang bcas cho ga
NK010(tha)014:641: gcig gis gzugs brnyan me long gnyis la dus gcig
NK010(tha)014:642: tu shar ba ltar sgom pa'i lugs ltar na dzapa
NK010(tha)014:643: kha dbye ba ma byas kyang rung ste /
NK010(tha)014:644: byed na gsal skyor tsam du bsgoms nas bdag mdun gyi rnam dbye phyed par bya /
NK010(tha)014:645: 'on kyang sgrub thabs rgyas 'bring ltar bskyed rim gyi dus bdag mdun 'jug pa gcig la /
NK010(tha)014:646: bzlas pa'i mgor dzapa kha phye nas dam ye rnam
NK010(tha)014:647: pa tha dad du byed pa 'di gsang sngags snga
NK010(tha)014:648: 'gyur ba'i ring lugs su snang zhing /
NK010(tha)014:649: don gyi cha nas 'gal ba 'du ba ma yin kyang /
NK010(tha)014:650: gsar ma la bdag mdun bum gsum cho ga tha
NK010(tha)014:651: dad du byed pas kha zer bar byed pa ni
NK010(tha)014:652: don la rton mi rton la dpyad pa med pa'i
NK010(tha)014:653: rang lta mchog 'dzin gyi phyogs su bslan no //
NK010(tha)014:654: de lta bu'i bdag mdun la bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor /
NK010(tha)014:656: phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor te phur pa rang
NK010(tha)014:657: lugs dkyil 'khor gsum gyi tha snyad sgra ji bzhin
NK010(tha)014:658: pa rdzogs la / lar bsnyen phur bkod phyin chad dkyil 'khor gsum gyi brda' chad tshang zhing /
NK010(tha)014:659: sras mchog la mang nyung sna tshogs phur pa'i rgyud
NK010(tha)014:660: sde rgya mtsho lta bu nas gsungs pas gang yang
NK010(tha)014:661: mi 'gal lo // bzlas bya'i sngags ni /
NK010(tha)014:662: dza h+aum a gsum bsnan pa man ngag gi dgongs pa yin la /
NK010(tha)014:663: rgyud las 'di ltar bshad pa sngar ma mthong ste /
NK010(tha)014:665: dkyil 'khor gsum la tha dad re //
NK010(tha)014:666: dgug dang gsad dang gzhom pa'o //
NK010(tha)014:667: k+ai la ya h+aum phata bar du //
NK010(tha)014:668: gzhug pa'i snying po tha dad do //
NK010(tha)014:670: yang na dza las gyur ba'o //
NK010(tha)014:671: gsad pa m+aa ra ya gsum la //
NK010(tha)014:672: gzhom zhing brdeg pa a ko ta //
NK010(tha)014:673: gcig gis gcig bskul 'od zer ni //
NK010(tha)014:675: zhes pas khong khra 'jug pa'i sdom 'ba' zhig bstan pas so //
NK010(tha)014:677: tshogs kyi sgrub pa chen po ni gzhan don dang
NK010(tha)014:678: phrin las rnam pa bzhi sogs la dmigs pa'i phyir
NK010(tha)014:680: shel gyis rengs pa nyid la yin //
NK010(tha)014:681: dbang la tsan+dana dmar po nyid //
NK010(tha)014:682: lung thang gis ni mngon spyod do //
NK010(tha)014:683: ni rang su ni sdang ba la //
NK010(tha)014:684: rta yi rus pas skrod pa nyid //
NK010(tha)014:685: bram ze'i rus pas dgug pa nyid //
NK010(tha)014:686: glang chen rus pas ser ba la //
NK010(tha)014:687: ma he nyid kyis gsad pa'o //
NK010(tha)014:688: rengs par 'o ma btung ba nyid //
NK010(tha)014:689: dbang la ra yi sha za'o //
NK010(tha)014:690: bsad pa la ni shwa na'i sha /
NK010(tha)014:691: dgug pa la ni bzhi mnyam nyid //
NK010(tha)014:692: bskrad pa la ni glang por brjod //
NK010(tha)014:696: dam tshig sems dpa'i 'od zer spros //
NK010(tha)014:697: ye shes sems dpa'i thugs rgyud bskul //
NK010(tha)014:698: thugs bskyed dam bca' rjes dran nas //
NK010(tha)014:699: dam pa'i tshul gyis 'od zer bkye //
NK010(tha)014:700: dam tshig mkha' la ri dwags 'grogs pa dang //
NK010(tha)014:701: mar me gnyis dag gcig tu sdom pa bzhin //
NK010(tha)014:702: dam tshig 'od zer bskul bas gnyis med gcig tu phab //
NK010(tha)014:704: bde bar gshegs pa'i thugs dam bskul //
NK010(tha)014:705: thugs bskyed thugs dam rjes dran nas //
NK010(tha)014:706: dam pa'i tshul gyi 'od zer bkye //
NK010(tha)014:707: snga chu'i steng du phyi chu phab //
NK010(tha)014:708: dkar dmar mthing gsum gnas su gnas //
NK010(tha)014:709: so mal lcags la ngar blud bzhin //
NK010(tha)014:710: dbang dang byin rlabs nus pa thob par bskul //
NK010(tha)014:712: bde mchog bde sbyor b+ha ga'i klong yangs nas //
NK010(tha)014:713: rab dgyes byang chub sems kyi dngos grub bskul //
NK010(tha)014:714: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga ni char bzhin 'bab //
NK010(tha)014:715: mchod pa'i bye brag rnams la mchod par bskul //
NK010(tha)014:716: zhes pa yan gyis rang don du rgyal ba mchod cing thugs dam bskul ba'i don bstan nas /
NK010(tha)014:717: khro bo chen po de dag gis //
NK010(tha)014:718: bdud dang bar du gcod pa rnams //
NK010(tha)014:719: bsgral te byang chub lam la bkod //
NK010(tha)014:720: rgyu drug 'khor ba'i sems can rnams //
NK010(tha)014:721: lus sems bral te 'khyams pa dang //
NK010(tha)014:722: ngan 'gro'i sgo dgag bde lam bkod //
NK010(tha)014:723: khro rgyal sku yi 'od zer gyi //
NK010(tha)014:724: steng 'og phyogs mtshams kun tu spro //
NK010(tha)014:725: de nas sems can thams cad kyang //
NK010(tha)014:726: rang rang nyon mongs kun sbyong byed //
NK010(tha)014:727: grol ba'i lam la bkod nas kyang //
NK010(tha)014:728: sdug bsngal thams cad des 'joms byed //
NK010(tha)014:730: don gnyis byed pa'i 'od zer spro bsdu'i dmigs pa sgrub thabs su bshad pa ltar dang /
NK010(tha)014:731: de yang sgrub pa'i dus grangs ma rdzogs kyang dngos
NK010(tha)014:732: grub kyi rtags gegs kyis bardzusa pa ma yin par
NK010(tha)014:733: nges pa brtan po byung na de ma thag dngos
NK010(tha)014:734: grub blang ba re byed pa'ang rten 'brel gyi gnad
NK010(tha)014:736: sgrub pa dag ni byed dus su //
NK010(tha)014:737: dngos grub rtags ni byung gyur na //
NK010(tha)014:738: the tshom med pa'i rtogs pas blangs //
NK010(tha)014:739: dngos grub chen po thob nas kyang //
NK010(tha)014:740: las rnams thams cad bya ba yin //
NK010(tha)014:743: bzlas pa byas pa'i 'bras bu ni //
NK010(tha)014:744: sgrub po nam mkhar 'gro ba dang //
NK010(tha)014:746: nam mkhar sgra brnyan 'byung ba dang //
NK010(tha)014:747: sgrub phur da ha'i sgra sgrogs dang //
NK010(tha)014:749: bar snang dag tu brtan par gnas //
NK010(tha)014:750: srin mo'i tshogs rnams 'du ba dang //
NK010(tha)014:751: sgrub pa'i man ngag phun tshogs bcas //
NK010(tha)014:752: gter rnams yod par smra ba dang //
NK010(tha)014:753: dril bas ri rab bsnyil ba dang //
NK010(tha)014:754: mtsho gling tshal rnams skem pa dang //
NK010(tha)014:755: btab pas nyi zla brtan par nus //
NK010(tha)014:756: 'di rnams byung na dngos grub rtags //
NK010(tha)014:759: 'od dang dri dang sgra ngan dang //
NK010(tha)014:760: rab rib mi brtan 'gyur ba can //
NK010(tha)014:761: rtags min dngos grub bar chad byed //
NK010(tha)014:762: rdo rje kha t+w+aam rnge'u chung dang //
NK010(tha)014:763: nyung dkar phur pa zhing lpags dang //
NK010(tha)014:764: gu gul dud pa btang bas dbyung //
NK010(tha)014:767: nyi khri bdun 'bum bgrangs nas kyang //
NK010(tha)014:768: lha rnams thugs dam bskul bar bya //
NK010(tha)014:769: khro bo chen po rnams la ni //
NK010(tha)014:770: nyi khri lnga stong bsnyen pa dang //
NK010(tha)014:772: srod thun la tshogs mchod rgyas pa re bya zhing /
NK010(tha)014:773: bye brag pa tshogs kyi 'khor lo'i tha snyad smos na /
NK010(tha)014:774: de nas rdo rje phur pa yi //
NK010(tha)014:775: tshogs kyi 'khor lo bshad par bya //
NK010(tha)014:776: sku yi dkyil 'khor bri bar bya //
NK010(tha)014:777: sna tshogs zas dang sna tshogs 'bru //
NK010(tha)014:778: sman gyi rnam pa gtor ma ni //
NK010(tha)014:779: glang po'am shing rtas 'gros pa'i tshad //
NK010(tha)014:780: brgya rtsa brgyad dang lha grangs bya //
NK010(tha)014:781: sha sna khrag sna brgya rtsa brgyad //
NK010(tha)014:782: spyan gzigs 'dod yon sna tshogs brgyan //
NK010(tha)014:783: sna tshogs 'bras bu'i tshogs rnams bsham //
NK010(tha)014:784: rnal 'byor pho mo g.yas dang g.yon //
NK010(tha)014:785: lus ngag brdas mtshon so sor mchod //
NK010(tha)014:786: lha sogs phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod //
NK010(tha)014:787: tshogs kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i tshe //
NK010(tha)014:788: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon la //
NK010(tha)014:789: mtshan ldan gzungs ma phul nas ni //
NK010(tha)014:790: gtso bo rnams la de bzhin mchod //
NK010(tha)014:792: rang rang gzungs dang bcas te mchod //
NK010(tha)014:793: mchod pa'i las byed dus brdas mtshon //
NK010(tha)014:794: gang zhig spyi bo ston pa na //
NK010(tha)014:795: de la rkang mthil bstan par bya //
NK010(tha)014:796: gang zhig smin ma 'degs byed na //
NK010(tha)014:797: de la mdzub mo bstan par bya //
NK010(tha)014:798: gang zhig lce ni bskyod bya ba //
NK010(tha)014:799: de la pad+ma bstan par bya //
NK010(tha)014:800: gang zhig mdzub mo ston pa na //
NK010(tha)014:801: de la lag pa sbyin par bya //
NK010(tha)014:802: gang zhig brang ni ston pa na //
NK010(tha)014:803: de la nu ma bstan par bya //
NK010(tha)014:804: gang zhig sor mo rnams ston la //
NK010(tha)014:805: de la lus ni bstan par bya //
NK010(tha)014:806: gang zhig a ho zhes brjod na //
NK010(tha)014:807: kye ma ho zhes rab tu brjod //
NK010(tha)014:808: a ti pu ho brjod pa la //
NK010(tha)014:809: pra ti pu ho brjod par bya //
NK010(tha)014:810: a ti dza zhes brjod pa la //
NK010(tha)014:811: pra t+aits+tsha zhes brjod par bya //
NK010(tha)014:812: sa ma ya s+t+wam brjod pa la //
NK010(tha)014:813: sa ma ho zhes brjod par bya //
NK010(tha)014:814: r+aa ho&a ham zhes brjod pa la //
NK010(tha)014:815: r+aa ga ya mi brjod par bya //
NK010(tha)014:816: kye zhes 'bod pa'i sgra sgrogs na //
NK010(tha)014:817: a ho zhes pa'i lan yang byin //
NK010(tha)014:818: su ra ti zhes brjod pa la //
NK010(tha)014:819: bza' zhing btung ba rab tu sbyin //
NK010(tha)014:820: sa ma dzahzhesa brjod pa la //
NK010(tha)014:821: lha rnams mchod cis rab tu sbyin //
NK010(tha)014:822: du du ra zhes brjod pa la //
NK010(tha)014:823: spang bar bya zhes rab tu brjod //
NK010(tha)014:824: de bzhin ngag gi sgra rnams kyang //
NK010(tha)014:825: dus 'di dag tu bya ba yin //
NK010(tha)014:827: bdud rtsi lnga yang rtog med bza' //
NK010(tha)014:828: sha dang khrag ni btung zhing bza' //
NK010(tha)014:829: der ni dam tshig can bzung zhing //
NK010(tha)014:830: dam tshig med dang nyams pa spangs //
NK010(tha)014:831: brtul zhugs chen po'i spyod pa yis //
NK010(tha)014:832: tshogs kyi 'khor lo rab tu bya //
NK010(tha)014:834: dam tshig nyams pa bskang ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)014:835: nang gi tshogs kyi 'khor lo bya //
NK010(tha)014:836: tshogs bsog bsod nams bskyed dus phyi //
NK010(tha)014:837: mi rtog ye shes bskyed dus su //
NK010(tha)014:838: gsang ba'i tshogs kyi 'khor lo bya //
NK010(tha)014:839: tshogs 'khor de gsum gang gis kyang //
NK010(tha)014:840: sgrib sbyong rnam grol lam la 'god //
NK010(tha)014:842: yab yum rigs lnga'i khrag 'thung dang //
NK010(tha)014:843: khro bcu yab yum phra men tshogs //
NK010(tha)014:844: mchod pas dngos grub shugs la 'byung //
NK010(tha)014:845: pho nya bka' nyan bsgo ba nyan //
NK010(tha)014:846: khams gsum nyon mongs kun sgrol byed //
NK010(tha)014:847: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub thob //
NK010(tha)014:848: rgyal po bram ze khyim bdag tshogs //
NK010(tha)014:849: dregs pa'i bsod nams dbang du 'du //
NK010(tha)014:851: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa sgrol //
NK010(tha)014:852: de phyir tshogs kyi 'khor lo yang //
NK010(tha)014:853: mkhas pas bya bar bshad pa yin //
NK010(tha)014:855: gsum pa las sbyor ram bsgrub pa chen po ni /
NK010(tha)014:856: sngon la dam can nye bar bsnyen pa byas nas /
NK010(tha)014:857: de nas sngags drug gi las sbyor bya ba'i tshul logs su yod do //
NK010(tha)014:858: de lta na'ang bsgrub bya dmigs bsal med pa la
NK010(tha)014:859: gtor ma dang mthun rdzas la brten nas dam can
NK010(tha)014:860: gyi bsnyen pa las rung tsam byed na /
NK010(tha)014:861: brub khung du zan ling bkod pa'i steng dam can lcam dral gyi spungs gtor bkod /
NK010(tha)014:863: gtor ma la shes pa gsum dang ldan pa las
NK010(tha)014:864: bsnyen pa'i tshe dkyil 'khor gyi mu ran la bka'
NK010(tha)014:865: sdod ltar gnas pa la gtso bo'i 'od zer gyis
NK010(tha)014:866: gzir bas drag po'i phrin las thogs med du byed
NK010(tha)014:867: par bsam la bzhi snying gcig dril gsum khri lnga
NK010(tha)014:868: stong bazla'o // de'i tshe sngon gyi phur pa mkhan
NK010(tha)014:869: po rnams la grags pa'i shes pa gsum gyi man
NK010(tha)014:870: stong bazla'o // ngag las / lhar shes pa ni
NK010(tha)014:871: thugs srog sngags phreng las byung ba'i 'od zer gyis
NK010(tha)014:872: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi lha tshogs mun khang du sgron
NK010(tha)014:873: me bteg pa ltar shin tu gsal ba nyid snang
NK010(tha)014:874: la rang bzhin med par rtsal sbyang /
NK010(tha)014:875: dgug gzhug tu shes pa ni /
NK010(tha)014:876: 'od zer gyi sne la pho nya dpag tu med pa spros /
NK010(tha)014:877: phyag rgya bzhis 'gugs 'ching bsdams myos byas te nya bo la bstim mo //
NK010(tha)014:878: chos nyid du shes pa ni /
NK010(tha)014:879: lha tshogs rnams las byung ba'i 'od zer gyis khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad dang /
NK010(tha)014:880: khyad par gzas pa po'i sdig sgrib skyong ba'i ngang
NK010(tha)014:881: la bdag gzhan du ma ro gcig tu bsres nas
NK010(tha)014:882: mnyam par 'jog / de ltar bsgrub pa thon pa'i rjes thog tu /
NK010(tha)014:883: tshogs tha ma dang 'brel bar las drug gi gdab las /
NK010(tha)014:884: spyir btang ba bsreg 'phang gnyis nas blangs la zhal bstab yan rdzogs par bya'o //
NK010(tha)014:886: dngos grub len chog gi mtshon cho ga'i rjes chog rnams dang /
NK010(tha)014:887: rgyal tho grol zhing thog mar dam gtsang dang 'phrad /
NK010(tha)014:888: de nas mtshams rim pas seng zhing gnas bsrung ba sogs spyi dang mthun no //
NK010(tha)014:889: gal te snyigs ma lnga'i rgud pa'i gzhan dbang las ldang mi nus pas /
NK010(tha)014:890: yi dam bzang po la las 'brel 'jog pa tsam
NK010(tha)014:891: gyis mos pas slob pa dag ni bsnyen phur dang
NK010(tha)014:892: / sman raka gtor gsum la brten nas /
NK010(tha)014:893: zla ba gcig tu bsnyen pa'i dmigs pa kho na dang /
NK010(tha)014:894: zla ba gnyis la nyer bsgrub dang sbrel zhing /
NK010(tha)014:895: zla ba gsum kar bzlas pa yig 'bru bcu bzhi
NK010(tha)014:896: pa kho na 'grus par bzlas pas bsnyen sgrub zung
NK010(tha)014:898: de yang dam can nye bsnyen sbrel na zhag bdun lhag pa la bzhi snying dril ba bzla zhing /
NK010(tha)014:899: rgyun du bzlas pa ma chag tsam dang /
NK010(tha)014:900: gtor bsngo byed pa dam tshig go //
NK010(tha)014:901: de dag su'ang rung ste rdo rje'i theg pa ni
NK010(tha)014:902: gsang nas spyad na 'grub pa yin pas yi dam
NK010(tha)014:905: rtog ge ba dang mig rnon mkhan //
NK010(tha)014:906: gsang sngags dngos grub snod ma yin //
NK010(tha)014:907: de la bshad na nyams chen yin //
NK010(tha)014:908: zhes pas gsang ba bsrung ba la bsgom zhing /
NK010(tha)014:909: rang bzhin lta ba'i dam tshig bzhi dran pa'i rtsi
NK010(tha)014:910: dang ma bral ba'i ngang nas spyod pa rgyun gyi
NK010(tha)014:914: le lo spang zhing gsang sngags kyi brda' bsrung /
NK010(tha)014:915: gal mdo nges pa'i dam tshig dkon mchog dang /
NK010(tha)014:916: gang zag gis ma khrel ba dang /
NK010(tha)014:920: kun nas nyams pa bzhi rnams spangs na /
NK010(tha)014:924: grags pa thob pa sogs shugs la 'byung ba la mthar phyin gyi rtags bzhi zhes bya ste /
NK010(tha)014:925: mdor na snying rje chen po dang /
NK010(tha)014:926: thabs la mkhas pas gzhan la phan 'dogs pa la
NK010(tha)014:927: dga' ba'i brtson pa mi lhod pa ni theg pa
NK010(tha)014:928: chen po gsang sngags kyi dam tshig rgya mtsho'i 'du
NK010(tha)014:929: sa'o // bstan pa'i gzugs brnyan cung zad yod dus 'dir //
NK010(tha)014:930: dad gus bskyed nas nyams su ma blangs na //
NK010(tha)014:931: ring por mi thogs bskyed rdzogs zab mo'i lam //
NK010(tha)014:932: nub rir phyogs pa'i mngon rtags mthong min nam //
NK010(tha)014:933: de phyir lhag pa'i bsam pa ga bur rdul //
NK010(tha)014:934: snga 'gyur rgyud sde'i nags klung la sman pa'i //
NK010(tha)014:935: chos tshul ri dwags lang tsho gsar ba'i dpyid //
NK010(tha)014:936: kun gyis mthong nas yang dag don rtogs shog /
NK010(tha)014:937: rwa ston sku skye rin po ches ljon shing gi
NK010(tha)014:938: yol go dang po la nee pa la'i dong tse'i
NK010(tha)014:939: tshom bu bkod nas nan tan gyis bskul ba'i ngor
NK010(tha)014:940: bka'i bsdu ba po rang nyid kyis so //
